<para id="fs-idm62954960">Draw the demand, marginal revenue, marginal cost, and average cost curves. Do they have the normal shapes?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm100082672">
<para id="fs-idm100082416">Yes, all curves have normal shapes.</para>
